### Get all albums
GET http://localhost:8080/albums

###

### Get album by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/1

###

### Create a new album (with existing artist reference)
POST http://localhost:8080/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Let It Be",
  "numberOfTracks": 12,
  "artist": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

###

### Create album without artist (will work but artist will be null)
POST http://localhost:8080/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Standalone Album",
  "numberOfTracks": 10
}

###

### Update an album
PUT http://localhost:8080/albums/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Abbey Road (Remastered)",
  "numberOfTracks": 17,
  "artist": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

###

### Delete an album
DELETE http://localhost:8080/albums/2

###
